{"tid":1679243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［置頂］仲有8日就到全民口罩日喇！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-28T05:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T23:59:57.000Z","uid":27026,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ff724c5062faf03998d978ce2c8102eb480a54","tid":1679243,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"為咗宣傳11.5全民口罩日，我由今日開始直到11月5號，每日都會開一個po倒數同提醒大家果日戴口罩，務求令到果日我要見到個個戴晒口罩返工返學放工放學！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本戴開嘅就繼續戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以做嘅野就係手人置頂呢個po，打個「推」、push、貼文宣圖等等，再身體力行啲嘅可以share埋出公海，同時我會收集呢個po嘅文宣圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11.5 全民口罩日！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/698d6bP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F698d6bP.jpg&h=363051c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emNVz5Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemNVz5Z.jpg&h=1c6de3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1grGZy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1grGZy.jpg&h=4afdf04a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b106bba9438f716ce677f27c4687cb5efda1764","tid":1679243,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a9ca3ab9a789d5862defe645b128cc4bf5a9da6e","tid":1679243,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl